The 'God Game' tag on SteamDB lists games where players assume the role of a deity, controlling various aspects of a world or civilization. In these games, players may create and destroy, shape the landscape, influence civilizations, and manipulate natural phenomena to achieve goals or respond to challenges. Players often have god-like powers to intervene in the lives of characters, control the elements, and set the course of history. God games can offer strategic depth and complexity, as players navigate ethical dilemmas, resource management, and diplomacy with entities within their domain. With an automated page update, gamers can easily browse this extensive collection to discover new titles and expand their godly repertoire.
